othing the EEG has no ionizing radiation it's much cheaperthan CT or MRI and the EEG brings in some money to my department  SLMR 21  Email jimzisfein@factorycom Jim Zisfein                                                                         " confidence="0.2" support="20" types="" sparql="" policy="whitelist">
